<h2>Be Dashboard - "Be the best version of yourself"</h2>

<%= render 'shared/side_menu' %>

<div id="graph" class="dashboard-section graph full-width">
  <h3>Graph of Inputs</h3>
  <p>7 categories of self-discovery and centeredness.</p>
  
  <div class="be-circle-container">
    <div id="centerPercentage" class="center-percentage">0%</div>
    <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="none" stroke="#444" stroke-width="10" />
      <circle id="progressCircle" cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="none" stroke="#64b5f6" stroke-width="10" stroke-dasharray="565.48" stroke-dashoffset="565.48" />
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="5" fill="#ffffff" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="heuristics-container">
    <h4>Centeredness Categories</h4>
    <div class="heuristics-grid">
      <div class="heuristic-column">
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>FOUNDATION</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Sila/Ethics</li>
            <li>Samadhi/Concentration</li>
            <li>Panna/Insight</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic1" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>VIRTUE</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Courage</li>
            <li>Compassion</li>
            <li>Curiosity</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic2" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>WHAT IS</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Awareness</li>
            <li>Body</li>
            <li>Mind</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic3" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="heuristic-column center-column">
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>HARMONY</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Profoundness</li>
            <li>Happiness</li>
            <li>Skillfulness</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic4" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="heuristic-column">
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>MIRROR</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Self</li>
            <li>Sensation</li>
            <li>Situation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic5" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>SKILL</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Conscious&nbsp;Mindfulness</li>
            <li>Honed Focus</li>
            <li>Open Awareness</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic6" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="heuristic">
          <h4>UNHAPPINESS</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Ignorance</li>
            <li>Craving</li>
            <li>Aversion</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="slider-container">
            <input type="range" id="heuristic7" min="0" max="100" value="0">
            <span class="heuristic-value">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="dashboard-grid">
  <div id="model" class="dashboard-section model">
    <h3>Model of geometry</h3>
    <p>A nested series of traingles glowing or not as we realise our nature and peace.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="practice" class="dashboard-section practice">
    <h3>Practice</h3>
    <p>Vipassana Meditation</p>
    <a href="https://www.dhamma.org/en/schedules/schdipa">10 day Vipassana Course</a>
  </div>

  <div id="analogy" class="dashboard-section analogy">
    <h3>Analogy</h3>
    <p>A best self eye and a series of lenses that distort our view of the world and our self. Where through the lens' we end up showing up on the earth, as our best self given our current perceptions.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="equation" class="dashboard-section equation">
    <h3>Equation of Mastery</h3>
        <p>Mastery of Presence (I Am with Peace) = (Input Acceptance * Maximise Equanimous Observing * Minimise Misery) + (Process of Learning * Inner Observation * Outer Realisation)</p>
  </div>

  <div id="metrics" class="dashboard-section metrics">
    <h3>Throughput Metrics for Be</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Centered: <span id="centeredPercentage">0</span>%</li>
      <li>Realised: <span id="realisedPercentage">0</span>%</li>
      <li>Mindfulness: <span id="mindfulnessPercentage">0</span>%</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .full-width {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .be-circle-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin: 1rem auto;
  }
  .center-percentage {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .heuristics-container {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .heuristics-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 15px;
  }
  .heuristic-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .center-column {
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .heuristic, .dashboard-section {
    background-color: #2c2c2c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .heuristic h4 {
    margin: 0 0 5px 0;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
  .heuristic ul {
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .heuristic li {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .slider-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .slider-container input[type="range"] {
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .heuristic-value {
    min-width: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }
</style>

